WEBVTT

00:01:38.959 --> 00:01:39.920
I have seen this child

00:01:41.799 --> 00:01:42.480
Where is he?

00:01:43.079 --> 00:01:44.200
Where is my brother?

00:01:44.920 --> 00:01:45.959
Hundred-Knowledge Villa

00:01:46.799 --> 00:01:47.680
Once you enter the Villa,

00:01:48.159 --> 00:01:49.680
you will find the answers you seek

00:01:57.239 --> 00:01:58.680
Do you want to avenge your brother?

00:02:05.159 --> 00:02:06.159
I do

00:02:10.159 --> 00:02:13.199
You look just like the Young Miss

00:02:26.919 --> 00:02:28.400
We had an agreement beforehand

00:02:29.759 --> 00:02:30.800
If we succeed,

00:02:31.960 --> 00:02:33.159
we escape together

00:02:35.599 --> 00:02:36.439
If we fail,

00:02:39.120 --> 00:02:40.479
someone must be sacrificed

00:02:44.719 --> 00:02:46.400
She went to her death willingly

00:02:57.439 --> 00:02:59.000
Zhao Yun can kill, too

00:03:01.479 --> 00:03:02.280
Well?

00:03:04.759 --> 00:03:05.719
Disappointed, aren't you?

00:03:16.680 --> 00:03:17.879
You have suffered for so many years

00:03:18.319 --> 00:03:19.000
Zhao Yun

00:03:26.039 --> 00:03:28.120
This is the peace lock you gave me back then

00:03:29.000 --> 00:03:29.719
I'm returning it to you

00:03:35.159 --> 00:03:36.159
It really works

00:03:38.759 --> 00:03:39.639
As long as you are safe

00:03:45.039 --> 00:03:45.560
Zhao Yun

00:04:01.719 --> 00:04:02.520
I am sorry

00:04:04.560 --> 00:04:05.360
My Zhao Yun

00:04:07.439 --> 00:04:08.879
should not have suffered so much hardship

00:04:11.199 --> 00:04:12.479
I have failed you

00:04:28.240 --> 00:04:29.000
So,

00:04:31.120 --> 00:04:32.120
you killed the Manor Lord,

00:04:34.800 --> 00:04:35.959
also for the sake of revenge?

00:04:41.360 --> 00:04:42.759
It was for that young constable

00:04:48.920 --> 00:04:50.279
In this Fengqi Courtyard,

00:04:51.279 --> 00:04:54.000
there is no shortage of high officials and nobles

00:04:55.720 --> 00:04:57.639
But the only one who wanted to redeem me

00:04:58.160 --> 00:04:59.639
was a young constable

00:05:02.720 --> 00:05:04.199
To redeem me,

00:05:06.000 --> 00:05:07.639
it would take 122 years

00:05:11.319 --> 00:05:13.079
But we were in love

00:05:14.360 --> 00:05:17.759
We swore to save enough money together,

00:05:20.439 --> 00:05:21.519
and fly far away

00:05:23.240 --> 00:05:24.920
Thinking back, it was truly absurd

00:05:51.199 --> 00:05:53.000
Siniang, you have finally arrived

00:05:53.199 --> 00:05:55.319
The distinguished guests are waiting for you in the hall

00:05:56.279 --> 00:05:57.839
Thank you, Master Liu, for recommending me

00:05:58.560 --> 00:06:00.279
Siniang, you are too polite

00:06:00.439 --> 00:06:02.199
To gain the Manor Lord's favor,

00:06:02.439 --> 00:06:04.680
I can also bask in your reflected glory, can't I?

00:06:05.959 --> 00:06:07.120
Siniang, please

00:06:07.879 --> 00:06:08.360
Alright

00:06:14.519 --> 00:06:16.160
After tonight's Hundred-Knowledge Banquet,

00:06:17.240 --> 00:06:18.560
I will have the money to redeem myself

00:06:19.480 --> 00:06:20.079
Wait for me

00:06:23.439 --> 00:06:25.680
I thought good days were coming

00:06:26.720 --> 00:06:27.639
I never expected

00:06:28.600 --> 00:06:30.800
that this was the beginning of my nightmare

00:06:54.759 --> 00:06:56.120
Wonderful

00:06:57.040 --> 00:06:57.720
Yes

00:07:47.279 --> 00:07:48.199
Lord Taiwei

00:07:48.800 --> 00:07:49.920
A spring night is precious

00:07:50.199 --> 00:07:51.399
This lowly one will not disturb you

00:08:06.680 --> 00:08:08.800
Such dark and hopeless days...

00:08:09.240 --> 00:08:10.639
I don't know how long they lasted

00:08:12.399 --> 00:08:14.519
I never saw the young constable again

00:08:15.959 --> 00:08:17.160
Until one day,

00:08:18.959 --> 00:08:20.800
I heard he came to the Villa to find me,

00:08:21.680 --> 00:08:23.240
and was killed by men sent by Master Liu

00:08:24.879 --> 00:08:25.959
That killer

00:08:27.040 --> 00:08:28.399
was named Zhang Shan

00:08:45.840 --> 00:08:47.159
Miss Xiao Bai

00:08:47.759 --> 00:08:49.159
are you looking for me?

00:09:18.480 --> 00:09:20.440
I... I'll be gentle

00:09:24.840 --> 00:09:25.639
No need

00:09:27.399 --> 00:09:28.279
I am used to the pain

00:09:37.639 --> 00:09:38.799
If you want to escape,

00:09:39.240 --> 00:09:40.320
I can help you

00:09:45.799 --> 00:09:47.960
Is a life of luxury not good enough?

00:09:49.600 --> 00:09:50.799
Why escape?

00:10:00.639 --> 00:10:01.639
If you do not escape,

00:10:03.440 --> 00:10:05.200
make those who have hurt you

00:10:05.879 --> 00:10:07.360
pay the price

00:10:14.720 --> 00:10:15.679
Miss Xiao Bai,

00:10:19.399 --> 00:10:20.759
why do you say this?

00:10:25.799 --> 00:10:26.759
Every day, Siniang,

00:10:26.759 --> 00:10:28.840
in the Golden Pigeon Wine you serve the Manor Lord,

00:10:29.159 --> 00:10:30.360
you have added something

00:10:31.080 --> 00:10:33.679
It happens to clash with the elixirs the Manor Lord takes

00:10:38.000 --> 00:10:39.399
Doing this, Siniang,

00:10:39.639 --> 00:10:41.559
how long will it take to get what you want?

00:10:43.320 --> 00:10:44.159
Five years?

00:10:45.480 --> 00:10:46.320
Ten years?

00:10:53.840 --> 00:10:55.360
Why don't we join forces?

00:10:57.000 --> 00:11:01.320
Let Heaven take these wicked men sooner

00:11:29.200 --> 00:11:30.360
Satisfying

00:11:38.080 --> 00:11:39.440
Satisfying